        <mxCell id="VTvKnRXI_Lt4VSYpTB3S-7" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;*Legenda&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(112, 112, 112);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(112, 112, 112);&quot;&gt;- Cor cinza&lt;/font&gt; indica pacotes com&amp;nbsp; código externo ao sistema. O&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;contrário representa código nativo/próprio do sistema.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;- &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 128, 128);&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; import &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/font&gt;: indica uma importação pública, onde os elementos do pacote fornecedor tornam-se visíveis para pacotes que dependem do pacote cliente.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;- &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 128, 128);&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; access &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/font&gt;: indica uma importação privada, onde o pacote cliente utiliza os elementos do fornecedor sem expô-los para outros pacotes externos.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
